WEBVTT

00:02.540 --> 00:04.380
Previously on
"A Million Little Things"...

00:04.380 --> 00:06.000
Jon: Friendship is the person
that you trust

00:06.000 --> 00:07.710
with your wallet and your wife
and your kids.

00:07.710 --> 00:10.040
It's being able
to have the hard conversations

00:10.040 --> 00:11.880
and be willing to listen.

00:11.880 --> 00:13.540
It's a million little things.

00:13.540 --> 00:17.380
You're not gonna believe this.
Jon killed himself.

00:17.380 --> 00:18.920
Rome: If you hadn't called
to tell me about Jon,

00:18.920 --> 00:20.710
I would be dead right now.

00:20.710 --> 00:23.290
I had a mouthful of pills
when I answered that phone.

00:23.290 --> 00:27.120
Eddie:
Jon always said, "Everything
happens for a reason."

00:27.120 --> 00:29.250
I can't find a reason for this.

00:29.250 --> 00:31.710
What is he doing here?
Men get breast cancer, too.

00:31.710 --> 00:33.880
[ Moans ]

00:33.880 --> 00:35.960
Obviously,
my boobs are fake.

00:35.960 --> 00:37.620
Obviously,
I'm okay with that.

00:37.620 --> 00:39.210
Eddie: And where
did you meet this one?

00:39.210 --> 00:40.790
10 bucks says
his breast cancer support group,

00:40.790 --> 00:42.040
and if I'm right,
you're gross.

00:42.040 --> 00:43.380
And you're
10 bucks richer.

00:43.380 --> 00:44.920
Regina:
Gary's an amazing friend.

00:44.920 --> 00:47.540
Underneath
that hot mess is...
A lukewarm mess?

00:47.540 --> 00:48.460
[ Laughter ]

00:48.460 --> 00:49.580
Gary:
When I spoke to Ashley,

00:49.580 --> 00:50.620
she said that up until then,

00:50.620 --> 00:52.420
it was a normal day
at the office.

00:52.420 --> 00:53.710
How does this happen?
Why did he do this?

00:53.710 --> 00:55.710
It makes no sense.

00:55.710 --> 00:59.120
Jon called you
at 12:27.

00:59.120 --> 01:01.750
I forgot my briefcase.
Didn't you notice I left it?

01:01.750 --> 01:03.250
Why is everyone an idiot?

01:03.250 --> 01:04.620
Gary: You and your wife
can't stand each other,

01:04.620 --> 01:05.750
but you'll never leave her.

01:05.750 --> 01:06.920
I'm in love
with someone.

01:06.920 --> 01:08.830
We can't do this.
Not now.

01:08.830 --> 01:10.080
What if he knew
about us?

01:11.920 --> 01:13.120
♪♪

01:13.120 --> 01:16.170
♪ Hey, hey, hey, hey ♪

01:16.170 --> 01:22.500
♪♪

01:22.500 --> 01:23.790
What, did you just
go for a run?

01:23.790 --> 01:24.920
Yes.

01:24.920 --> 01:25.750
That's sexy.

01:25.750 --> 01:27.170
[ Laughs ]

01:27.170 --> 01:28.580
What happened in here?
Are you moving?

01:28.580 --> 01:29.750
I just moved.

01:29.750 --> 01:31.420
[ Both moan ]

01:31.420 --> 01:33.000
Like switching apartments?

01:33.000 --> 01:36.250
Yeah. To one
that's not in Chicago.

01:36.250 --> 01:37.750
[ Grunts ]

01:37.750 --> 01:39.500
Chicago?
Yeah.

01:39.500 --> 01:41.580
I don't -- I don't know
anything about you.

01:41.580 --> 01:42.670
I know.
Isn't it great?

01:42.670 --> 01:44.460
Ohh!

01:44.460 --> 01:45.500
So, when
are you gonna unpack?

01:45.500 --> 01:47.170
Mm...

01:47.170 --> 01:49.830
As soon as you
take your shirt off during sex.

01:49.830 --> 01:51.460
That's fair.
Yeah.

01:51.460 --> 01:54.000
