01:54.000 --> 01:56.290
[ Whispers ] Hey.
Walk with quiet feet, buddy.

01:56.290 --> 01:57.710
We don't want to
wake Mommy up.

01:57.710 --> 01:59.620
Dad? Quick question?

01:59.620 --> 02:01.170
Yeah,
what is it, bud?

02:01.170 --> 02:04.380
-Why are there wars?
-What?

02:04.380 --> 02:08.040
Why do some countries
fight other countries?

02:08.040 --> 02:09.620
Well...bud,

02:09.620 --> 02:12.620
I think that
some people feel...

02:14.790 --> 02:16.210
Tell you what, can
we talk about this
in the morning?

02:16.210 --> 02:18.210
Ooh, can we have waffles
in the morning?

02:18.210 --> 02:20.210
Sure.
Set a reminder
on your phone.

02:20.210 --> 02:21.960
As soon as
you get into bed,

02:21.960 --> 02:23.120
I will set a reminder.

02:23.120 --> 02:25.210
Waffles.
And war.

02:25.210 --> 02:26.830
We have to
talk about war.

02:26.830 --> 02:28.330
Waffles and war.

02:28.330 --> 02:30.380
Can't wait.

02:30.380 --> 02:33.330
Dad,
where's your necklace?

02:33.330 --> 02:35.710
Delilah:
[ Giggles ]

02:35.710 --> 02:37.250
We need to get back.

02:38.500 --> 02:40.920
Do you think
that maybe someday

02:40.920 --> 02:42.170
we'll be able to do this

02:42.170 --> 02:45.330
not in the back
of your Lexus?

02:45.330 --> 02:46.710
Yeah.

02:48.580 --> 02:50.000
As soon as
we tell him.

02:52.670 --> 02:54.000
Theo:
Are you okay, Dad?

02:56.380 --> 02:57.830
Yeah, bud.

02:57.830 --> 02:59.040
I'm fine.

