the dance.

38:37.330 --> 38:38.830
Yes, I do.

38:38.830 --> 38:40.830
Actually, I always did.

38:40.830 --> 38:42.500
Your dad
was nervous about dancing,

38:42.500 --> 38:44.170
so he had me
secretly coach him.

38:44.170 --> 38:46.380
Made me go over
all the moves.

38:46.380 --> 38:48.670
Like I said,
when it comes to dancing,

38:48.670 --> 38:49.750
I'm the one
that people go to.

38:49.750 --> 38:54.580
I didn't say anything
'cause you picked Eddie.

38:54.580 --> 38:58.710
And I didn't know if I could
fill your father's shoes.

38:58.710 --> 39:00.580
But I'm the one
who should dance with you.

39:02.420 --> 39:05.250
I think
it's what he wanted.

39:05.250 --> 39:06.670
Oh, my God.

39:06.670 --> 39:07.670
No, it's okay,
it's okay.

39:07.670 --> 39:09.040
I'm really good.

39:09.040 --> 39:12.000
No.

39:12.000 --> 39:13.830
He didn't
forget about me.

39:15.500 --> 39:17.710
Mom, don't film this.
No, let her film it.

39:17.710 --> 39:18.790
People have to see
how good I am.

39:18.790 --> 39:21.420
He got so much better!

39:23.750 --> 39:26.460
Dad did have a plan.

39:26.460 --> 39:28.420
Yes, he did.

39:28.420 --> 39:35.210
♪♪

39:35.210 --> 39:38.210
Even though she picked me,
I can't do this.

39:39.580 --> 39:40.710
I love you.

39:40.710 --> 39:42.210
Stop saying that.
No, listen to me.

39:42.210 --> 39:45.250
I love you.
I love Jon.

39:45.250 --> 39:46.790
I love Sophie.

39:46.790 --> 39:51.460
I love everybody
but me right now.

39:51.460 --> 39:55.080
That's why I can't be the one
to dance with Sophie.

39:55.080 --> 39:57.290
Even if she never finds out,
I know.

39:57.290 --> 39:59.170
I know what we did.

40:01.420 --> 40:04.830
[ Cheers and applause ]

40:04.830 --> 40:07.250
She is on.

40:09.750 --> 40:11.460
Thanks.

40:11.460 --> 40:12.920
Of course.

40:16.080 --> 40:24.250
♪♪

